data.description: Only minutes from Burgaw, this 3 bedroom, 2 full bathroom home is situated on a secluded, almost 1 acre lot, A new roof, new HVAC, new hot water heater, and new well pump were installed in 2022, giving peace of mind to the new buyers.  Ample windows throughout the home make it feel open and airy, and a cozy living room fireplace with built-ins is perfect for those cool nights. A large, open-concept kitchen with ample countertop space and cabinets make entertaining a breeze. Luxury vinyl flooring has been installed in the living spaces. The master bedroom suite is incredibly spacious and offers dual vanity sinks and a large garden soaking tub. Step outside to your private, fenced-in backyard with a storage shed.
